    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>##使用hexo搭建你的github博客<br><a href="http://www.cnblogs.com/liuxianan/p/build-blog-website-by-hexo-github.html" target="_blank" rel="external">http://www.cnblogs.com/liuxianan/p/build-blog-website-by-hexo-github.html</a></p>
<h3 id="1、准备条件"><a href="#1、准备条件" class="headerlink" title="1、准备条件"></a>1、准备条件</h3><ul>
<li>首先你得有一个自己的github账号，没有的话去注册一个吧。</li>
<li>其次你的电脑上需要安装nodeJs和npm，这是前提条件。</li>
<li>第三，作为一个开发者，git怎么能缺少呢，安装一个git for windows客户端吧。</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="2、Hexo的一些常用指令"><a href="#2、Hexo的一些常用指令" class="headerlink" title="2、Hexo的一些常用指令"></a>2、Hexo的一些常用指令</h3><p>①修改hexo主题<br><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">首先查找hexo主题，比如Next, 打开git命令窗口</div><div class="line">git clone https:<span class="comment">//github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next.git themes/Next</span></div><div class="line">--themes/Next表示存到这个文件夹下</div><div class="line">然后打开_config.yml找到theme主题，修改成theme: Next</div><div class="line">然后使用命令hexo g #生成</div><div class="line">           hexo s #启动服务</div><div class="line">如果出现一些莫名问题：使用hexo clean清除再生成           </div><div class="line">访问地址：http:<span class="comment">//localhost:4000/</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>②常用命令<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;code class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;pre&gt;</div><div class="line">hexo g #生成</div><div class="line">hexo s #启动服务</div><div class="line">hexo d #上传</div><div class="line">hexo new &apos;my-first-blog&apos; #创建md文件</div><div class="line">&lt;/pre&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;/code&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>③错误讲解<br><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">执行hexo d的时候经常都会有</div><div class="line">ERROR Deployer not found: git错误</div><div class="line">原因是hexo3.0以后将server单独分出来了，而我们需要自己去下载</div><div class="line">这里建议cmd命令下载</div><div class="line">指令为：npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"></div><div class="line">deploy:</div><div class="line">  type: git</div><div class="line">  repository: git<span class="meta">@github</span>.com:wenni328/wenni328.github.io.git</div><div class="line">  branch: master</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">https://segmentfault.com/a/1190000009544924  next布局</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">``` &#123;% codeblock [title] [lang:language] [url] [link text] %&#125; code snippet &#123;% endcodeblock %&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
